      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"small actions\" don't change the fact that the math doesn't add up. it feels like just putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. i look at the future and i just see nothing. it's hard to find a reason to keep going through the cycle of work and stress when you know the entire foundation is just going to crumble anyway. doesn't it feel like we're just prolonging the inevitable?",
